
1  Eka Holoferno nonyiso jotichne mondo oter Judith kama noselosnee chiemo. Nowacho ni mondo omi Judith chiemo gi divai moa e mesane owuon, 
2  to Judith nowachone niya, “Ok onego acham chiemogo nikech dipo ka aketho chikwa. Chiemo ma asebirogo oroma chamo.” 
3  Holoferno nopenje niya, “To kapo ni chiembi orumo, to ere kuma dwayudnie chiemo moko, nikech waonge gi jou moko modak kodwa ka?” 
4  Judith nodwoke ni, “Kik iparri kuom wachno ruodha, nimar nayud ka Ruoth Nyasaye osemiyo atieko gima adwaro ni mondo atim kapok chiembani orumo.”


5  Bang’ mano, jolweny ma jokony Holoferno notero Judith e hema moro machielo mi nonindo kanyo nyaka dier otieno, to nochiew ka chiegni chopo sa apar mar otieno. 
6  Noyudo osekwayo Holoferno niya, “Ruodha, yie igol chik mondo wan gi jatichnani wayud thuolo mar wuok e kambi ka wadhi lamo Nyasaye.” 
7  Omiyo Holoferno nosechiko jotichne mondo kik gisinde wuok. Kamano Judith nobet e kambi kuom ndalo adek, kendo nodhi e holo mar Bethulia otieno kotieno kolwokore e soko mane oseketie jorit cha. 
8  To pile kane odwogo malo e kambi, nokwayo Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasach Israel mondo okonye reso joge kaka noseketo chunye mondo otim. 
9  Eka nodok e hembe ka osepuodhore, kendo nobet kuno nyaka chop ocham chiembe godhiambo.

Judith odhi e nyasi mar Holoferno


10  Chieng’ mar ang’wen Holoferno notimo nyasi, moluongoe mana jotichne owuon kende, to ne ok oluongo jotelo moko mag lweny. 
11  Eka nowacho ni Bagoas jatichne mabwoch mane rito gige niya, “Dhiyo iho dhako ma nyar jo-Hibrania mirito cha, mondo obii ochiem kendo ometh kodwa. 
12  Wabiro yudo wichkuot ka waweyo dhako maber machal kama odhi adhiya ma ok wang’eye maber. Ka ok wasere mi oyie kodwa, to ji duto nonyierwa!” 
13  Bagoas nowuok oweyo Holoferno modhi ir Judith, owachone niya, “Bende in nyako ma jaber kendo mapod tin kama, diyie dhiyo e nyasi ruodha? Ka iyie timo kamano, to ibiro bet e kom mar duong’ momanyore gi ruodha, kimadho kodwa divai makelo mor, kichalo kaachiel kuom nyi Asuria mobet e od ruoth Nebukadnezar.” 
14  Judith nodwoke niya, “An to an ng’a, ma dadagi timo gima ruodha dwaro ni mondo atim? Ayie timo duto modwaro, kendo amor timo kamano nyaka chieng’ thona.”


15  Kane osewacho kamano, noa malo morwakore, kendo nolichore gi gik moko duto mabeyo ma dhako nyalo lichorego. Eka jatichne notelo nyime mi odhi opedho pien e nyim Holoferno. Ne en pien mane Bagoas osemiyo Judith mondo obedie pile kochiemo. 
16  Bang’e Judith nodonjo mobet kama noseikne. Kane Holoferno onene, remb ringre noridore, kendo chunye noling’ore. Gombo maduong’ mar terruok kode nomake. Chutho, chakre chieng’ mane okwongo nenoe judith, nosebet komanyo kinde monyalo losoe kode, mondo oyiene. 
17  Nowacho ni Judith niya, “Methi kendo ibed mamor nyarwa.” 
18  Judith to nodwoke ni, “Ruodha, amor ahinya mondo atim kamano, nimar nyaka ne nywola, pok abetie gi mor machal ma an-go kawuononi!” 
19  Eka nokawo chiemo mane jatichne oseloso, mochiemo, kendo ometho e nyim Holoferno kanyo. 
20  To Holoferno ne mor kode ahinya, omiyo nomadho divai mathoth moloyo kaka nosemadho e ndalo mamoko duto.

